<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.3">
<l>vāḻak kaṇṭōm vantu kāṇmiṉ toṇṭīrkāḷ</l>
<l>kēḻal ceṅkaṇ māmu kilvaṇṇar maruvumūr</l>
<l>ēḻaic ceṅkā liṉṟuṇai nāraik kiraitēṭi</l>
<l>kūḻaip pārvaik kārva yalmēyum kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, we saw [how] to prosper; come and see!</l>
<l>Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where a silly thing grazes in a dark field,</l>
<l>Hunting with rapid glances for food for [her] sweet, red-legged stork mate,</l>
<l>Is the city where the red-eyed one the hue of a dark cloud, the boar appears.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
